Class DeclarationOfMajority

java.lang.Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.asn1.ASN1Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.asn1.isismtt.x509.DeclarationOfMajority
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.asn1.ASN1Choice, com.distrimind.bouncycastle.asn1.ASN1Encodable, com.distrimind.bouncycastle.util.Encodable
public class DeclarationOfMajority extends com.distrimind.bouncycastle.asn1.ASN1Object implements com.distrimind.bouncycastle.asn1.ASN1Choice
A declaration of majority. 
           DeclarationOfMajoritySyntax ::= CHOICE
           {
             notYoungerThan [0] IMPLICIT INTEGER,
             fullAgeAtCountry [1] IMPLICIT SEQUENCE
             {
               fullAge BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE,
               country PrintableString (SIZE(2))
             }
             dateOfBirth [2] IMPLICIT GeneralizedTime
           }

fullAgeAtCountry indicates the majority of the owner with respect to the laws of a specific country.
